{"tid":1301983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該戴番口罩","createTime":"2019-07-09T19:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T23:20:23.000Z","uid":122197,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"889befb94204323e4fd1a560e9a7a80bcd1740d1","tid":1301983,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:39:39.000Z","msg":"早兩日發夢，見到入夜之後街上面仲有好多人，大部份都戴口罩，但<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">總有部分人可能覺得無咩野所以唔帶</span></strong>，直頭有啲情侶好似當行街咁唔帶口罩慢慢行。。。大佬呀可唔可以保護下自己？有咩事發生起上黎真係會奶野架。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我夢入面都見到街上好多人影相，有啲係普通市民，有啲鬼鬼崇崇唔知咩人黎，但總無可能唔俾所有人影相。同埋一般市民影相，係一種民間紀錄，紀錄低曾經有一班人努力過。再加上記者都會影相同拍片，無可能下下都就到鏡頭唔影到任何一個樣。戴番口罩，唔好令記者難做。"},{"pid":"6c44fe3ec6c15eaceb9c110efc029f7002316439","tid":1301983,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:42:23.000Z","msg":"［重要必看］ 7.7 九龍區遊行及旺角黑夜時序<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301227</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28a772030998aaa7c5eb911beb67f00b6c2506f","tid":1301983,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b7ccb5743a41f5f360b264e2741066b7a44b56b","tid":1301983,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:57:38.000Z","msg":"如果真係覺得戴住焗，就買黑色透氣海綿料個款"},{"pid":"4beb6c90a5040faa5125d454c42b2501153858fb","tid":1301983,"uid":44038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T21:22:51.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b54bd83a1c6dc5fda2300a5136a4eedca894a2fa","tid":1301983,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:14:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6246939af44d9ac75cba6602b5348b531c023581","tid":1301983,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T23:20:23.000Z","msg":"好多共碟影大頭相<br />\n如果你出黎夢遊又番大陸就一定死緊"}]}